{"tid":296734,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[蘇格蘭撚入]點樣去isle of skye同loch ness?","createTime":"2017-06-24T22:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T12:59:52.000Z","uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6dbc81458545c935817d226647f3aa488e329a","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T22:50:05.000Z","msg":"無車牌<br />\n係咪要跟團?<br />\n由Inverness出發嘅團有無團去曬isle of skye同loch ness?<br />\n1日去曬定點? (我無乜時間)<br />\n同埋有無團推介?<br />\n唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fbb4951a26bd11bd8a70ca542183d4273da0f0","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:05:07.000Z","msg":"我會去4日蘇格蘭<br />\n諗住去Edinburgh同Inverness<br />\n我上網睇團有團係3 day tour由Edinburgh出發包去Isle of Skye同Loch Ness<br />\n有團係1 day tour由Inverness出發包Isle of Skye同Loch Ness<br />\n邊個好d?<br />\nInverness唔去有無損失?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73db885122000cd29390f6f1a6e501c4e528a94b","tid":296734,"uid":6307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:10:45.000Z","msg":"係呀冇車highlands好難玩<br />\n得跟團但好少1日過咁快<br />\n通常都2/3日<br />\n好天風景真係勁靚"},{"pid":"228d8b0ac8a46a79a5cd5e58720923e51053ab9e","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:11:01.000Z","msg":"我個時間嗰間rabbies嘅3 day tourfull撚咗 屌<br />\n1 day會唔會太急?"},{"pid":"e304209b5f102bc967a85dea83d6cd3cd30da072","tid":296734,"uid":6307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會去4日蘇格蘭<br />\n諗住去Edinburgh同Inverness<br />\n我上網睇團有團係3 day tour由Edinburgh出發包去Isle of Skye同Loch Ness<br />\n有團係1 day tour由Inverness出發包Isle of Skye同Loch Ness<br />\n邊個好d?<br />\nInverness唔去有無損失?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1日睇得唔多 會勁趕<br />\n睇你想走馬看花定點<br />\nInverness比起skye差好遠"},{"pid":"44eb3ae7c5f2503f6a300c11cbda04689f2b0143","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:39:33.000Z","msg":"有無人跟過Timberbush嘅3 day tour?<br />\n好唔好?"},{"pid":"9b0d970ca72cdf9c83c790768fa49f15878610d1","tid":296734,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"1日真係太chur 我同意頭先巴打講既3日Highlands+Skye 我覺得如果齋睇景既話唔去Inverness都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n我覺得蘇格蘭d景大多係荒涼得黎又壯闊<br />\n最靚既都係Loch Lomond上去Glencoe個段路 同埋Old Man of Storr個邊 唔睇真係好可惜(given that天氣好) <br />\n<br />\n湖個d唔係話唔靚 但個個其實都一鳩樣既 如果之前已經睇過英國d湖(例如係Lake District)  唔睇Loch Ness/Loch Lomond都唔會覺得特別可惜<br />\n<br />\n另外有d地方例如係Glennfinnan Viaduct都唔錯 不過要較啱時間等有蒸氣火車經過 另外Skye上面有地方可以坐船出海睇海豹定唔知海獅<br />\n<br />\n除左Rabbies之外仲有一個叫Discover Scotland既都有3day tour 近期join過我覺得都唔錯 你都可以研究一下"},{"pid":"3bc9236dd80d4f2c0dbe1a7c02ee6f2e4c66dd22","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:08:29.000Z","msg":"唔該曬兩位靚巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我再睇睇<br />\n我朋友唔鍾意跟團但佢又唔幫手plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我偏向跟3 day tour 佢就1 day 屌"},{"pid":"656b91491387d1cb5a280fd9d60dec3faf65ec1a","tid":296734,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"Glasgow 去Fort William段路都已經夠做有凸，再去前面其實冇乜意思<br />\n我係渣車嘅，但沿途都見好多巴士同埋旅行團，梗有一啲啱你嘅"},{"pid":"1ae91b53ec40b78062d87764b5a4e1aa9a8007e4","tid":296734,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Glasgow 去Fort William段路都已經夠做有凸，再去前面其實冇乜意思<br />\n我係渣車嘅，但沿途都見好多巴士同埋旅行團，梗有一啲啱你嘅</blockquote><br />\n我諗住個團帶我去邊就去邊<br />\n包isle of skye同loch ness就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facf939364cc3f00b9148a961df815aaef1f10b0","tid":296734,"uid":28267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人跟過Timberbush嘅3 day tour?<br />\n好唔好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上年join 完 timberbush 3 day tour 去晒isle of Skye 同loss ness. 行程安排都唔會太趕，最後個日仲帶埋我地去smoky whisky 廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知其他tour 嘅導遊係咪咁，但我join 個次個佢都 Scotland English 口音勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完全聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76bc6a69490714622869a8bd8377861e1500198","tid":296734,"uid":28267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人跟過Timberbush嘅3 day tour?<br />\n好唔好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上年join 完 timberbush 3 day tour 去晒isle of Skye 同loss ness. 行程安排都唔會太趕，最後個日仲帶埋我地去smoky whisky 廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知其他tour 嘅導遊係咪咁，但我join 個次佢d Scotland English 口音勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完全聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c1bf1eacde452df9686f8fe3191b6e6cacd61ced","tid":296734,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"我係報三日團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔太自由同有d追馬看花，<br />\n但真心不枉此行....好正🤤"},{"pid":"07a6925c35bc46822bde8a09e6d208c3a